channel.title: Need Help With Server Compiler, Please help me
channel.description:
I have TestScape and when i click in "compile" i wait like 10 secs and in the command window says this:
"Note: stream.java uses or overrides deprecated API. Note:Recompile with -Xlint:deprecation for details. Press any key to continue..."
Please i need someone who can tell me what to do, i have the JDK Update 2, and i set my variables.
PLZ HELP TY
